OL,3,CDriver charged after HGV crashes down
OL,4,Cembankment onto rail line
OL,6,FA HGV driver has been charged after
OL,7,Fhis vehicle crashed down an embankment
OL,8,Fonto the railway line.
OL,10,FThe incident happened just before 8am,
OL,11,Fnear Gretna. No trains have been able
OL,12,Fto run between Carlisle and Dumfries
OL,13,Fall day as emergency services cleared
OL,14,Fthe lorry off the line so Network Rail
OL,15,Fcould begin repairs.
OL,17,FThe A74(M) southbound near Gretna was
OL,18,Fdown to one lane and the slip road at
OL,19,FJunction 22 closed to allow for the
OL,20,Frecovery of the vehicle.
