OL,6,FThe driver was taken to hospital in
OL,7,FDumfries as a precaution and has since
OL,8,Fbeen charged by Police Scotland with a
OL,9,Froad traffic offence.
OL,11,FA Scottish Ambulance Service
OL,12,Fspokesperson said, "We dispatched one
OL,13,Fambulance and one paramedic response
OL,14,Funit to the scene. One patient was
OL,15,Ftransported to Dumfries and Galloway
OL,16,FRoyal Infirmary."
