OL,6,FScotRail said all stations between
OL,7,FDumfries and Carlisle "cannot be
OL,8,Fserved by train" and warned that was
OL,9,Flikely to continue "for the remainder
OL,10,Fof the day".
OL,12,FPhil Campbell, ScotRail Customer
OL,13,FOperations Director, said: "ScotRail
OL,14,Fservices between Glasgow Central and
OL,15,FCarlisle via Dumfries are currently
OL,16,Fdisrupted.
