OL,6,F"To keep people moving, customers with
OL,7,Fvalid train tickets can travel on
OL,8,Falternative routes where possible,
OL,9,Fwith replacement buses also in
OL,10,Foperation. Anyone delayed by 30
OL,11,Fminutes or more can claim compensation
OL,12,Fthrough our Delay Repay Guarantee."
OL,14,FThe West Coast Mainline and Glasgow
OL,15,Fand South Western Line were initially
OL,16,Fclosed as a precaution but reopened a
OL,17,Fshort time after. Avanti West Coast
OL,18,Fand Transpennine Express services
OL,19,Fbetween Glasgow, Lockerbie and
OL,20,FCarlisle are still running.
